air-s20-network-additions-as-of-07jan20/|work=Routesonline|date=8 January 2020}}</ref> [[Kyiv International Airport|Kiev\u2013Zhuliany]] (begins 29 May 2020),<ref>{{cite news|last1=Liu|first1=Jim|title=Ellinair S20 Kyiv operation changes|url=https://www.routesonline.com/news/38/airlineroute/288582/ellinair-s20-kyiv-operation-changes/|work=Routesonline|date=8 January 2020}}</ref> [[Lviv Danylo Halytskyi International Airport|Lviv]], [[Vnukovo International Airport|Moscow\u2013Vnukovo]], [[Odesa International Airport|Odessa]] (begins 3 June 2020),<ref name=EllinairS20/> [[Pulkovo Airport|Saint Petersburg]] (resumes 2 May 2020),<ref name=EllinairS20/> [[Warsaw Chopin Airport|Warsaw\u2013Chopin]] (resumes 24 May 2020)<ref name=EllinairS20/>\n<!-- -->\n| [[Enter Air]] | '''Seasonal charter:''' [[Katowice Airport|Katowice]],<ref name=\"TUI.pl\">{{cite web|title=Charter flights |url=https://www.tui.pl/tanie-bilety-lotnicze?pm_source=MENU&pm_name=Bilety_czarterowe |accessdate=4 September 2018}}</ref> [[Warsaw Chopin Airport|Warsaw\u2013Chopin]],<ref name=\"TUI.pl\"/> [[Copernicus Airport Wroc\u0142aw|Wroc\u0142aw]]<ref name=\"TUI.pl\"/>\n<!-- -->\n| [[Eurowings]] | '''Seasonal:''' [[Berlin Tegel Airport|Berlin\u2013Tegel]], [[Cologne Bonn Airport|Cologne/Bonn]], [[Dusseldorf Airport|Dusseldorf]], [[Hamburg Airport|Hamburg]], [[Munich Airport|Munich]], [[Salzburg Airport|Salzburg]], [[Stuttgart Airport|Stuttgart]]\n<!-- -->\n| [[Finnair]] | '''Seasonal:''' [[Helsinki Airport|Helsinki]]\n<!-- -->\n| [[FlyOne]] | '''Seasonal charter:''' [[Chi\u0219in\u0103u International Airport|Chi\u0219in\u0103u]]<ref name=\"Tez.mo\"/>\n<!-- -->\n| [[Freebird Airlines Europe]] | '''Seasonal charter:''' [[Leipzig/Halle Airport|Leipzig/Halle]] (begins 2 May 2020)<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.lvz.de/Nachrichten/Wirtschaft/Wirtschaft-Regional/Tui-schickt-Freebird-Europe-nach-Leipzig-Halle-Airbus-A320-wird-in-Schkeuditz-stationiert|title=Tui sends Freebird Europe to Leipzig / Halle - Airbus A32