ljana]], [[Munich Airport|Munich]], [[Oslo Airport, Gardermoen|Oslo\u2013Gardermoen]], [[Palma de Mallorca Airport|Palma de Mallorca]] (begins {{date|2020-6-27}}),<ref>{{cite news |last1=Liu |first1=Jim |title=Israir adds Palma Mallorca seasonal service in S20 |url=https://www.routesonline.com/news/38/airlineroute/289333/israir-adds-palma-mallorca-seasonal-service-in-s20/ |accessdate=5 February 2020 |work=Routesonline |date=5 February 2020}}</ref> [[Poprad\u2013Tatry Airport|Poprad-Tatry]], [[Rhodes International Airport|Rhodes]], [[Riga International Airport|Riga]] (begins 25 May 2020),<ref name=6HS20>{{cite web|last1=Liu|first1=Jim|title=Israir schedules new Eastern Europe routes in S20|url=https://www.routesonline.com/news/38/airlineroute/288941/israir-schedules-new-eastern-europe-routes-in-s20/|website=Routesonline|date=21 January 2020}}</ref> [[Leonardo da Vinci\u2013Fiumicino Airport|Rome\u2013Fiumicino]], [[Rovaniemi Airport|Rovaniemi]], [[Salzburg Airport|Salzburg]], [[Skopje International Airport|Skopje]] (begins 11 June 2020),<ref name=6HS20/> [[Sofia Airport|Sofia]], [[Stuttgart Airport|Stuttgart]], [[Tbilisi International Airport|Tbilisi]], [[Tenerife South Airport|Tenerife\u2013South]], [[Thessaloniki Airport|Thessaloniki]], [[Tirana International Airport N\u00ebn\u00eb Tereza|Tirana]], [[Tivat Airport|Tivat]], [[Varna Airport|Varna]], [[Zvartnots International Airport|Yerevan]], [[Zakynthos International Airport|Zakynthos]], [[Zurich Airport|Z\u00fcrich]] (begins 29 June 2020)<ref>{{cite web|last1=Liu|first1=Jim|title=Israir adds Zurich service in S20|url=https://www.routesonline.com/news/38/airlineroute/288467/israir-adds-zurich-service-in-s20/|website=Routesonline|date=2 January 2020}}</ref>\n<!-- -->\n| [[KLM]] | [[Amsterdam Airport Schiphol|Amsterdam]]\n<!-- -->\n| [[Korean Air]] | [[Incheon International Airport|Seoul\u2013Incheon]]\n<!-- -->\n| [[LATAM Chile]] | [[Arturo Merino Ben\u00edtez International Airport|Santiago de Chile]], [[S\u00e3o Pa