an\u2013Queen Alia]]\n<!-- -->\n| [[RwandAir]]| [[Kigali International Airport|Kigali]]\n<!-- -->\n| [[Ryanair]] | [[Athens International Airport|Athens]], [[Orio al Serio International Airport|Bergamo]], [[Berlin Sch\u00f6nefeld Airport|Berlin\u2013Sch\u00f6nefeld]] (begins 29 March 2020), [[Bologna Guglielmo Marconi Airport|Bologna]], [[Budapest Ferenc Liszt International Airport|Budapest]], [[Brussels South Charleroi Airport|Charleroi]], [[Karlsruhe/Baden-Baden Airport|Karlsruhe/Baden-Baden]], [[Krak\u00f3w John Paul II International Airport|Krak\u00f3w]], [[Marseille Provence Airport|Marseille]], [[Memmingen Airport|Memmingen]], [[Paphos International Airport|Paphos]], [[Pozna\u0144\u2013\u0141awica Airport|Pozna\u0144]], [[Leonardo da Vinci\u2013Fiumicino Airport|Rome\u2013Fiumicino]], [[Sofia Airport|Sofia]], [[Thessaloniki Airport|Thessaloniki]], [[Vilnius Airport|Vilnius]], [[Warsaw Modlin Airport|Warsaw\u2013Modlin]]<br> '''Seasonal:''' [[Henri Coand\u0103 International Airport|Bucharest]]\n<!-- -->\n| [[S7 Airlines]] | [[Tolmachevo Airport|Novosibirsk]] (resumes {{date|2020-4-2}})<ref>{{cite news |last1=Liu |first1=Jim |title=S7 adds Novosibirsk \u2013 Tel Aviv service from April 2020|url=https://www.routesonline.com/news/38/airlineroute/287917/s7-airlines-adds-novosibirsk-tel-aviv-service-from-april-2020/ |accessdate=4 December 2019 |work=Routesonline |date=4 December 2019}}</ref>\n<!-- -->\n| [[Sichuan Airlines]] | [[Chengdu Shuangliu International Airport|Chengdu]]\n<!-- -->\n| [[SkyUp]] | [[Lviv Danylo Halytskyi International Airport|Lviv]], [[Kharkiv International Airport|Kharkiv]],<ref name=\"SkyUp\">{{cite web|url=https://skyup.aero/uk/|title=SkyUp|website=skyup.aero}}</ref> [[Zaporizhia International Airport|Zaporizhia]]\n<!-- -->\n| [[Smartwings]] | [[V\u00e1clav Havel Airport Prague|Prague]]\n<!-- -->\n| [[Sun d'Or]] | [[Krak\u00f3w John Paul II International Airport|Krak\u00f3w]], [[Tbilisi International Airport|Tbilisi]] <br>'''Seasonal:''' [[A